足全年都唔奇<br />\n<br />\nOt一星期補得果十幾個鐘 你嘅工時一定唔只 補得足就唔係big 4啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3649883b5d7c98db7d9d69b1a2874d7b6d1dc2","tid":341744,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點會冇</blockquote><br />\n有就有<br />\n一定係少數</blockquote><br />\n7少陣啦 SA2 未Q 都30k up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger sa3都貼住40k啦</blockquote><br />\n計時薪幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係吹水...但計返時薪都應該幾高...有ot補返 仲有slack season 你估真係忙吹全年咩 幾個月架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左12月year end 仲有其他月份架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你估真係有slack 咩 忙足全年都唔奇<br />\n<br />\nOt一星期補得果十幾個鐘 你嘅工時一定唔只 補得足就唔係big 4啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇命水架咋 個個中曬4個year end咩 我諗大部份人中2個only  ot好睇你自己有冇爭取 交唔交到貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人認為"},{"pid":"99d03f0ffbcf2abea3d9a274bb07d48da7beef61","tid":341744,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點會冇</blockquote><br />\n有就有<br />\n一定係少數</blockquote><br />\n7少陣啦 SA2 未Q 都30k up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger sa3都貼住40k啦</blockquote><br />\n計時薪幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係吹水...但計返時薪都應該幾高...有ot補返 仲有slack season 你估真係忙吹全年咩 幾個月架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左12月year end 仲有其他月份架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你估真係有slack 咩 忙足全年都唔奇<br />\n<br />\nOt一星期補得果十幾個鐘 你嘅工時一定唔只 補得足就唔係big 4啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\